Revision history for PAL

0.001    2026-02-06
         - Initial release
         - Complete PAL (Perl Async for Linux) framework in single distribution
         - PAL::Loop - Event loop framework (was Linux::Event)
         - PAL::Uring - Async I/O (was IO::Uring::Easy)
         - PAL::Fanotify - Filesystem monitoring (was Linux::Fanotify::Easy)
         - PAL::Uevent - Hardware events (was Linux::Uevent::Easy)
         - Unified namespace and cohesive ecosystem
         - Comprehensive documentation
